76
00:11:56,236 --> 00:12:00,284
Kita akan bertemu pada 05:30.
Tolong jangan terlambat.

77
00:12:30,315 --> 00:12:32,874
Semuanya sudah siap, Bapa?

78
00:12:32,944 --> 00:12:35,412
Mari kita berdoa bersama.

79
00:14:18,627 --> 00:14:20,549
Ya tuhan.

80
00:14:32,425 --> 00:14:33,760
Ayo.

81
00:14:34,252 --> 00:14:37,287
